1
00:00:05,965 --> 00:00:08,633
Aukeratu kolorea eta zuri beltzaren artean
beheko "Bertsio alternatiboak"-ekin.

2
00:00:08,634 --> 00:00:11,971
Gailu bateragarrietan erabilgarri.

3
00:00:25,151 --> 00:00:27,945
<i>Zein unibertso zen hau
galdetu zidan behin batek,</i>

4
00:00:29,071 --> 00:00:32,324
<i>ez dut galdera bitxi hori ahaztu
urte hauetan guztietan.</i>

5
00:00:33,743 --> 00:00:37,163
<i>Nik ezagutzen nuen bakarra zela esan nion,</i>

6
00:00:37,955 --> 00:00:39,957
<i>eta hori ez da aldatu.</i>

7
00:00:40,374 --> 00:00:42,125
DEBEKUA INDARREAN
SILVERMANENTZAT ETEKINAK

8
00:00:42,126 --> 00:00:44,211
<i>Ezohiko gizona naiz?</i>

9
00:00:44,712 --> 00:00:45,671
<i>Bai.</i>

10
00:00:46,172 --> 00:00:47,757
<i>Gizon arrunta naiz?</i>

11
00:00:48,257 --> 00:00:49,549
<i>Bai.</i>

12
00:00:49,550 --> 00:00:50,759
<i>Biak naiz.</i>

13
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,177
<i>Eta bat ere ez.</i>

14
00:00:52,178 --> 00:00:53,220
<i>Denok bezala.</i>

15
00:00:55,806 --> 00:00:56,891
<i>New York.</i>

16
00:01:00,186 --> 00:01:01,771
<i>Hemen hazi nintzen,</i>

17
00:01:03,522 --> 00:01:05,149
<i>hemen ikasi nuen borrokan…</i>

18
00:01:08,110 --> 00:01:09,820
<i>eta hemen maitemindu nintzen.</i>

19
00:01:13,741 --> 00:01:15,367
<i>Ez dut akats hori errepikatuko.</i>

20
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:23,082
<i>Armiarma izan ohi nintzen, hiriko heroia.</i>

21
00:01:23,083 --> 00:01:26,921
<i>Beti erne eta arazoak konpontzeko prest.</i>

22
00:01:44,188 --> 00:01:46,816
<i>Ruby hil zenean bukatu zen hori.</i>

23
00:01:58,744 --> 00:02:00,913
<i>Udaberrian ezkontzekoak ginen.</i>

24
00:02:01,789 --> 00:02:04,874
<i>Eraztun bat erosi nuen dena ondo egiteko.</i>

25
00:02:04,875 --> 00:02:07,253
<i>Baina ezin izan nion eman.</i>

26
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,464
{\an8}RUBY J. WILLIAMS
ABENDUAK 18, 1890 - MAIATZA

27
00:02:16,136 --> 00:02:21,308
<i>Rubyk behin esan zidan
botereak erantzukizuna dakarrela.</i>

28
00:02:22,518 --> 00:02:25,855
{\an8}<i>Bera izan zen inoiz izan nuen
erantzukizunik handiena,</i>

29
00:02:27,106 --> 00:02:28,482
<i>eta huts egin nion.</i>

30
00:02:30,276 --> 00:02:32,152
<i>Armiarmak huts egin zion.</i>

31
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:39,243
<i>Horren ostean, ez nuen botererik nahi,
ez eta erantzukizunik.</i>

32
00:02:42,746 --> 00:02:45,666
<i>Gizon arrunta bilakatu nintzen berriz.</i>

33
00:02:47,793 --> 00:02:50,129
<i>Hori duela bost urte izan zen.</i>

34
00:04:05,788 --> 00:04:08,165
{\an8}MARVEL KOMIKIETAN OINARRITUA

35
00:04:39,571 --> 00:04:40,614
Zer deritzozu?

36
00:04:45,119 --> 00:04:47,286
Bete-betean asmatu duzu.

37
00:04:47,287 --> 00:04:48,955
Nahiko lerdena zara.

38
00:04:48,956 --> 00:04:50,958
Ikusmen kaskarra daukazu gero.

39
00:04:52,167 --> 00:04:53,043
Barregarria zara.

40
00:04:53,919 --> 00:04:55,378
Ezkonduta zaude?

41
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:57,714
- Ez.
- Lastima.

42
00:04:57,715 --> 00:04:59,173
Ni bai.

43
00:04:59,174 --> 00:05:01,342
Horrek ez dit eragotziko ondo pasatzea.

44
00:05:01,343 --> 00:05:02,844
Ulertzen?

45
00:05:02,845 --> 00:05:04,054
Baietz uste dut.

46
00:05:04,722 --> 00:05:07,515
Zure senarrak ere ulertzen duenean,
esan deitzeko.

47
00:05:07,516 --> 00:05:09,308
B. REILLE IKERKETAK
DETEKTIBE PRIBATUA

48
00:05:09,309 --> 00:05:10,144
Ados.

49
00:05:14,064 --> 00:05:16,025
Barkatu, jauna!

50
00:05:17,026 --> 00:05:18,819
- Kapela ahaztu duzu.
- Mila esker.

51
00:05:20,237 --> 00:05:23,532
Niri segika jarraitzen baduzu,
gaizki bukatuko duzu.

52
00:05:24,158 --> 00:05:25,409
Beti bezala.

53
00:05:27,077 --> 00:05:28,370
Addison!

54
00:05:49,767 --> 00:05:50,683
Barkatu, lagun.

55
00:05:50,684 --> 00:05:53,478
Ez, Addison.

56
00:05:53,479 --> 00:05:56,273
Zu jarraitzeko
eta tiro egiteko ere gai naiz.

57
00:05:59,777 --> 00:06:00,861
Kaka!

58
00:06:09,453 --> 00:06:12,164
- Ondo al dago?
- Ai ene. Hilda dago?

59
00:06:19,338 --> 00:06:21,255
Jauna, ez zenuen…

60
00:06:21,256 --> 00:06:23,258
Nora joan dira? Nondik?

61
00:06:31,934 --> 00:06:34,645
STANDARD OIL ENPRESA

62
00:06:59,128 --> 00:07:01,712
Ez da nire errua
jende arriskutsua zapuztu baduzu.

63
00:07:01,713 --> 00:07:05,050
Berandu da
eta demaseko kiratsa dago hemen.

64
00:07:05,592 --> 00:07:07,219
Abisatu dizut.

65
00:07:08,137 --> 00:07:09,138
Zer?

66
00:07:18,147 --> 00:07:19,857
Erre egingo zara.

67
00:07:27,906 --> 00:07:29,783
Jesus, Maria eta Jose!

68
00:07:35,581 --> 00:07:36,497
Ez!

69
00:07:36,498 --> 00:07:37,332
ERREKORRA

70
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:39,209
Jainko maitea!

71
00:08:07,571 --> 00:08:10,657
PATRICK DONEGAL
DETEKTIBE PRIBATUA

72
00:08:11,325 --> 00:08:12,534
Ondo da.

73
00:08:14,328 --> 00:08:16,079
Gizon horrek su hartu du!

74
00:08:16,705 --> 00:08:18,164
Hamaika ikusteko ere.

75
00:08:18,165 --> 00:08:19,624
Susmatu behar nuen

76
00:08:19,625 --> 00:08:22,043
Tipoa jarraitzeagatik
50 eskaini didatenean.

77
00:08:22,044 --> 00:08:24,212
Winstonek kontratatu zaitu?

78
00:08:24,213 --> 00:08:26,757
- Bai.
- Kabroiak 30 $ baino ez dizkit eskaini.

79
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,343
Trago bat behar dut. Nahi?

80
00:08:30,344 --> 00:08:33,012
Noski. Ezer garestirik ez. Soilik dauzkat…

81
00:08:33,013 --> 00:08:36,600
Hiru dolar. Zatoz, Donegal.
Taberna on bat ezagutzen dut.

82
00:08:37,434 --> 00:08:40,479
Neska ere aurkitu dezakezu
burutik jotakoak gogoko badituzu.

83
00:08:42,064 --> 00:08:45,567
Baietz esan behar,
halako batekin ezkonduko naiz eta.

84
00:08:51,156 --> 00:08:53,616
- Egun on.
- Ez hainbeste.

85
00:08:53,617 --> 00:08:57,245
Nola-halako eguerdia da
eta arratsak ez du itxura onik.

86
00:08:57,246 --> 00:09:00,248
- Kaferik nahi?
- Baduzu ezer gogorragorik?

87
00:09:00,249 --> 00:09:02,625
Hori galdetzen diot beti senarrari.

88
00:09:02,626 --> 00:09:05,503
- Bota hemen bertan.
- Ezin da hori egin.

89
00:09:05,504 --> 00:09:06,796
Inork deitu du?

90
00:09:06,797 --> 00:09:11,175
Horretarako telefonoa ordaindu behar duzu.
Ordura arte, papergaineko bat da.

91
00:09:11,176 --> 00:09:12,469
Zer moduz Addisonena?

92
00:09:15,138 --> 00:09:16,265
Itzel.

93
00:09:17,766 --> 00:09:19,183
Addison hilda dago.

94
00:09:19,184 --> 00:09:22,228
- Zuk…
- Ez, beste bat izan da.

95
00:09:22,229 --> 00:09:24,272
Hiri madarikatu hau.

96
00:09:24,273 --> 00:09:25,523
Irekita dago?

97
00:09:25,524 --> 00:09:27,400
- Ez.
- Bai.

98
00:09:27,401 --> 00:09:28,401
Deitu dut, baina…

99
00:09:28,402 --> 00:09:32,363
Reilly jaunak nahiago du
aurrez-aurre hitz egitea.

100
00:09:32,364 --> 00:09:34,615
Ez duzu uste, jauna…

101
00:09:34,616 --> 00:09:37,703
- Carmedy jauna.
- Aurrera, Carmedy jauna.

102
00:09:38,537 --> 00:09:39,871
Nire emaztea da.

103
00:09:50,841 --> 00:09:53,010
Diru asko duzu, Carmedy jauna?

104
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:56,637
Ez hainbeste.

105
00:09:56,638 --> 00:09:58,515
Orduan, oso adimentsua izango zara.

106
00:10:02,561 --> 00:10:04,895
Telefonoz hitz egiten
entzun dut eguerdian.

107
00:10:04,896 --> 00:10:08,316
Gaur zortzietan batuko da
dena delako horrekin.

108
00:10:08,317 --> 00:10:10,276
Tokia ere dakit. Begira.

109
00:10:10,277 --> 00:10:13,195
Prest datozen bezeroak dira onenak.

110
00:10:13,196 --> 00:10:15,281
Orduan, bai? Kasua hartuko duzu?

111
00:10:15,282 --> 00:10:17,616
Carmedy,
eguneko 10 $ da nire prezioa, eta…

112
00:10:17,617 --> 00:10:19,952
Argazkiak lortuko dituzu?

113
00:10:19,953 --> 00:10:23,831
Argazkirik gabe
nire hitza eta haren hitza bakarrik daude.

114
00:10:23,832 --> 00:10:26,042
Ziur naiz susmoak ez direla egia, jauna,

115
00:10:26,043 --> 00:10:27,793
baina bestela bada, ez kezkatu.

116
00:10:27,794 --> 00:10:29,713
- Ben argazkilari trebea da.
- Onena.

117
00:10:33,091 --> 00:10:34,008
10 $ eguneko.

118
00:10:34,009 --> 00:10:35,760
Gehi gastuak.

119
00:10:35,761 --> 00:10:38,346
Janetek hartuko ditu zure datuak
eta aurrerakina.

120
00:10:38,347 --> 00:10:42,433
Zatoz etzi
eta nahi duzun hori emango dizut.

121
00:10:42,434 --> 00:10:43,518
Eskerrik asko.

122
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:47,981
Zatoz, Carmedy jauna.
Datuak eta aurrerakina hartuko ditut.

123
00:10:51,568 --> 00:10:55,363
"Leherketa Standard Oilen",
irakurri berria.

124
00:10:55,364 --> 00:10:58,532
"Leherketa Standard Oilen".

125
00:10:58,533 --> 00:11:02,287
Leherketa, hemen, Standard Oilen!

126
00:11:17,636 --> 00:11:20,054
Barkatu berandu iristeagatik. Lana nuen.

127
00:11:20,055 --> 00:11:24,934
Antza, beste mafioso batek
Silvermaneren aurka jardun du.

128
00:11:24,935 --> 00:11:27,144
Bere etxea erre zuen duela pare bat gau,

129
00:11:27,145 --> 00:11:31,065
bere gizonetako sei hil zituen,
eta hala ere ihes egin zuen agureak.

130
00:11:31,066 --> 00:11:33,526
Finn Byrneri gustatuko zaio
Silvermane deitzea?

131
00:11:33,527 --> 00:11:37,696
Izenak garrantzia eta hilezkortasuna
ematen dizkiolakoan?

132
00:11:37,697 --> 00:11:39,949
Halako dirutzarekin,
dei nazazu nahi duzuna.

133
00:11:39,950 --> 00:11:41,952
Ozpin-pepino handia da hori.

134
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:45,956
Zer duzu hor? Beste emazte iruzurti bat?

135
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:49,708
Hori utzi zenuen.

136
00:11:49,709 --> 00:11:53,045
Ez diot aspaldian Janeti ordaindu.
Eskaleek ezin dute aukeratu.

137
00:11:53,046 --> 00:11:55,297
Zuk aukeratu zenuen eskale izatea.

138
00:11:55,298 --> 00:11:58,301
- Jainkoarren, Ben.
- Robbie, ez hasi. Berriz ez.

139
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,887
Begiratu duzu zure ingurura?

140
00:12:01,888 --> 00:12:03,390
Hiria hankaz-gora dago.

141
00:12:04,015 --> 00:12:08,519
Armiarma desagertu zenetik
Silvermaneren esku dago hiria.

142
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:12,481
Krimena gailendu da,
eta polizia erosita dauka.

143
00:12:12,482 --> 00:12:13,774
Jendeak…

144
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:16,695
heroi bat behar du.

145
00:12:19,948 --> 00:12:23,284
Zorte ona opa diet.

146
00:12:23,285 --> 00:12:26,121
- Zu zinen…
- Badakit nor nintzen.

147
00:12:28,665 --> 00:12:30,834
Eta badakit nor naizen orain.

148
00:12:31,585 --> 00:12:34,545
Beti egongo da Silvermane bat, Robbie.

149
00:12:34,546 --> 00:12:36,173
Ez du zentzurik borrokatzeak.

150
00:12:36,923 --> 00:12:38,883
Zer pentsatuko luke Rubyk

151
00:12:38,884 --> 00:12:40,635
horrela hitz egiten entzungo balizu?

152
00:12:53,315 --> 00:12:55,275
Ruby aspalditik dago hilda,

153
00:12:57,235 --> 00:12:59,821
ez dit axola zer pentsatuko zuen.

154
00:13:03,992 --> 00:13:06,577
ZUGAN SINISTEN DUT!
BOZKATU BERRIZ MORRIS ALKATEA

155
00:13:06,578 --> 00:13:08,954
Kaixo, Frankie. Goiz zabiltza gaur.

156
00:13:08,955 --> 00:13:10,832
Kaixo, Reilly, zer moduz?

157
00:13:13,877 --> 00:13:16,670
Lapurtzeko trebezia hobetzen ibili naiz,

158
00:13:16,671 --> 00:13:18,256
Bai? Zer moduz doa?

159
00:13:19,841 --> 00:13:21,009
Zer deritzozu?

160
00:13:24,930 --> 00:13:25,930
Andereñoak, e?

161
00:13:25,931 --> 00:13:28,849
- Zer dakizu zuk?
- Asko. Oso azkarra naiz.

162
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:31,060
Ba orduan eskolara joan beharko zenuke.

163
00:13:31,061 --> 00:13:33,604
Zertarako? A gehi B berdin C.

164
00:13:33,605 --> 00:13:35,689
Matematikan ez dago hizkirik.

165
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:37,233
Donegal, Reilly naiz.

166
00:13:37,234 --> 00:13:39,528
Bart gertatu zenaz hitz egin behar dugu.

167
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:43,197
<i>Zer proposamen daukazu niretzat?</i>

168
00:13:43,198 --> 00:13:45,366
Gizon bat hil zenuen bart.

169
00:13:45,367 --> 00:13:47,743
Arazoak ekar ditzake aurrerago,

170
00:13:47,744 --> 00:13:49,370
baina aukera bat izan daiteke.

171
00:13:49,371 --> 00:13:52,122
Kontratatu gintuen
tipoa ikertu beharko genuke

172
00:13:52,123 --> 00:13:54,084
zergatik harrapatu nahi zuen jakiteko.

173
00:13:57,128 --> 00:13:58,296
Planik duzu?

174
00:13:59,214 --> 00:14:00,422
Halako zerbait.

175
00:14:00,423 --> 00:14:03,008
Biharko 9:00etarako
etorri zaitezke mozkortu gabe?

176
00:14:03,009 --> 00:14:05,178
Kaixo, lerdena. Aspaldiko.

177
00:14:07,097 --> 00:14:08,390
Bihar goizerako?

178
00:14:09,432 --> 00:14:10,267
Noski.

179
00:14:11,685 --> 00:14:13,269
<i>Arratsaldeko argitaraldia.</i>

180
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,603
SILVERMANEREN ETXEA SUTAN!

181
00:14:14,604 --> 00:14:16,272
"Barruko arropan salbatu zen!"

182
00:14:16,273 --> 00:14:17,606
Mila esker, jauna.

183
00:14:17,607 --> 00:14:19,025
Argitaratu berria!

184
00:14:19,651 --> 00:14:22,027
<i>"Barruko arropan salbatu zen!"</i>

185
00:14:22,028 --> 00:14:24,321
<i>"Armiarma desagertu zenetik,</i>

186
00:14:24,322 --> 00:14:27,283
<i>Silvermanek dauka hiriaren kontrola,</i>

187
00:14:27,284 --> 00:14:30,035
<i>bera oztopatzen duen edonor akabatzen du.</i>

188
00:14:30,036 --> 00:14:34,498
<i>baina gizon ausart bat
saiatu zen izuaren erreinua amaitzen,</i>

189
00:14:34,499 --> 00:14:37,877
<i>Silverameren etxeari su emanez
bera lo zegoen bitartean.</i>

190
00:14:38,712 --> 00:14:40,796
<i>Baina agure kabroi hori ez zenez hil,</i>

191
00:14:40,797 --> 00:14:44,718
<i>prestatu Silvermanek eta haren gizonek
eragingo duten sarraskirako.</i>

192
00:14:45,552 --> 00:14:49,680
<i>Armiarma hemen balego, bederen,
gu erokeria honetatik salbatzeko".</i>

193
00:14:49,681 --> 00:14:51,057
Arraioa, Robbie.

194
00:14:51,683 --> 00:14:53,435
Utzi behingoz.

195
00:15:32,849 --> 00:15:35,351
Arratsalde on, jauna. Zer behar duzu?

196
00:15:35,352 --> 00:15:38,020
Boris Karloffentzat gauza bat daukat.

197
00:15:38,021 --> 00:15:41,106
- Barkatu, lagun. Karloff ez da hemen bizi.
- Bai horixe.

198
00:15:41,107 --> 00:15:44,861
Bere izen faltsua emango zuen, Stein.

199
00:15:45,987 --> 00:15:48,782
Frank N. Stein.

200
00:15:51,868 --> 00:15:55,455
Lasai, ez kezkatu. Banoa.

201
00:16:47,549 --> 00:16:49,926
- Ez duzu zertan hori egin.
- Badakit.

202
00:17:01,312 --> 00:17:02,522
Orduan ados gaude.

203
00:17:05,108 --> 00:17:06,735
Kideak gara orain.

204
00:17:07,569 --> 00:17:10,320
Elkar ezagutu behar genuke.

205
00:17:10,321 --> 00:17:14,533
- Ez, hori ez da… Ez!
- Tira, eman zerbait.

206
00:17:14,534 --> 00:17:16,660
- Utzi bakean!
- Ba etorri.

207
00:17:16,661 --> 00:17:17,746
Etorri nirekin.

208
00:17:24,377 --> 00:17:25,420
Zer arraio?

209
00:17:36,681 --> 00:17:38,183
B. REILLY
DETEKTIBE PRIBATUA

210
00:17:43,062 --> 00:17:45,315
- Goiz etorri da.
- Zu zatoz berandu!

211
00:17:46,274 --> 00:17:48,026
Zoaz.

212
00:17:51,279 --> 00:17:52,279
Egun on, Winston.

213
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:54,531
Kaferik nahi duzu, edo terik?

214
00:17:54,532 --> 00:17:57,659
Edo biak eskatu nahi dituzu,
lehena zein datorren ikusteko?

215
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,620
Utzi txorakeriak, Reilly.

216
00:17:59,621 --> 00:18:02,664
Addison non dagoen omen dakizu,
hartu dirua eta bota.

217
00:18:02,665 --> 00:18:04,917
Prezioa igo egin da.

218
00:18:04,918 --> 00:18:06,252
Barkatu?

219
00:18:07,170 --> 00:18:09,880
Beste detektibeari
50 $ eskaini omen zenizkion,

220
00:18:09,881 --> 00:18:12,425
ez dizut tutik esango
200 $ baino gutxiagorengatik.

221
